name: Consent
file_txt:
በብሔራዊ መታወቂያ መርሃግብር ቅድመ ምዝገባ ወቅት ስለ እኔ የተሰበሰበው መረጃ የእኔን -
• ስም
• የትውልድ ቀን
• ፆታ
• አድራሻ
• የመኖሪያ ሁኔታ
• ሰነዶች
በተጨማሪም ይህ መረጃ የተለያዩ አገልግሎቶችን ለማግኘት ወይም የህግ ግዴታዎችን ለመወጣት ማንነቴን ለማጣራት እንደሚከማች እና እንደሚሰራ ተረድቻለሁ ፡፡ ለዚህ መረጃ መሰብሰብ ፈቃዴን እሰጣለሁ ፡፡

name: Template for Onscreen Acknowledgment
file_txt:
1. Once you registered online and booking, go to nearby enrollment center or you can go directly enrollment center
2. Keep handy supporting documents such as proof of identity and a proof of address, for example, kebele ID card, Passport, Driver license, etc.
3. Get an application form and fill all the required details. Once you submit application form and other supporting documents at the enrollment center, your biometric data will be taken by the official present at the center This will include an impression of fingerprints of your both hands, your iris and your photo.
4. After all the documents and biometric data are checked, you will get an acknowledgement slip of your enrolment having a 20-digit enrolment number on it which will help you keep a check on the status of your application
5. You can use the registration number and time provided in the acknowledgement slip to keep a track of your card.

name: Consent
file_txt:
I understand that the data collected about me during pre-registration by the said authority includes my -  
•                     Name
•                     Date of birth
•                     Gender
•                     Address
•                     Residence Status
•                     Contact details
•                     Documents
I also understand that this information will be stored and processed for the purpose of verifying my identity in order to access various services, or to comply with a legal obligation. I give my consent for the collection of this data for this purpose.
